{
  "text": "One possible solution to the information retrieval problem comes from the application of a recommender system which can offer a personalized response according to the preferences and needs of each user. Very good reviews can be found in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The most important aspects to take into consideration will be related with sorting the query results.",
  "citation_candidates": [
